OL,7,FA man from has been sentenced to 22
OL,8,Fyears in prison after being convicted
OL,9,Fof a series of rapes against women and
OL,10,Fyoung girls.
OL,12,FBrian Guest, 65, was jailed at
OL,13,FStafford Crown Court after being found
OL,14,Fguilty of rape, sexual assault and
OL,15,Findecent assault against his victims,
OL,16,Fwhich included children.
OL,18,FThe offences took place over a period
OL,19,Fof 37 years.
