OL,7,Fsay they came to light when a
OL,8,Fcomplaint was made against Guest in
OL,9,FOctober 2022, leading to an
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FSeveral complainants came forward and
OL,13,Freported him for rape and sexual
OL,14,Fassaults, which took place in a number
OL,15,Fof different settings.
OL,17,FGuest was put on trial and found
OL,18,Fguilty at Wolverhampton Crown Court in
OL,19,FJune last year. He was jailed for more
OL,20,Fthan 20 years on 23 January 2024.
