OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Nadia Cooper, from
OL,8,FWest Midlands Police's Investigations
OL,9,Fteam, said: "This was an appalling
OL,10,Fsequence of abuse in which Brian Guest
OL,11,Fabused his victims.
OL,13,F"Thanks to their bravery, we were able
OL,14,Fto build a case to bring him to
OL,15,Fjustice and hopefully grant them some
OL,16,Fmeasure of closure.
OL,18,F"We would urge anyone who knows or
OL,19,Fthinks they were a victim of sexual
OL,20,Fabuse in the past to contact us and
OL,21,Ftell us your story.
